data.name: URINE BAGS - STANDARD TYPE
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- Polyethylene (PE) Body
- PVC and DEHP-FREE PVC Tubing
- Polypropylene (PP) Clamps, Caps and Hangers

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- PVC and DEHP-FREE PVC
- Customized Printing
- T-Cross Outlet
- Single / Double Hangers
- Ridged Universal Connector
- Needle and Needle free Sampling Port
- With and Without Sliding Clamp

## PERFORMANCE
- 2 Litters Capacity
- Non-Flow Return Valve
- Clear, flexible, kink-resistant inlet PVC tubing
- Highly Transparent
- Capacity: 2000ml
- Type: pyriform; latex free, with 100%silicone blue outlet
and with folding clamp, with needle sample port,
with anti-reflux valve, with finger guard clamp
- Inlet tube: O.D10mm; 100cm length
